{"tid":1259483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好推啲分化post上熱門 睇到會好心淡","createTime":"2019-06-26T14:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:01:26.000Z","uid":20696,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"147b5127b0e31994aa64e57c63e2c249de6fa105","tid":1259483,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"大家都唔係第一次發夢<br />\n圍得都係有決心知有風險<br />\n點會無諗到鍵盤戰士講嘅野<br />\n經過上次網上嗌散水嘅事<br />\n大家應該有反省<br />\n唔係成日以為自己網上睇得最清楚<br />\n有下一步嘅人有勇無謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信佢地唔會真係純粹為一時衝動冒咁大風險<br />\n<br />\n唔認同可以講理據 可以提醒<br />\n但唔好人黎就質疑人 屌人<br />\n覺得危險 夜 少人 點解唔係去幫手 <br />\n而係要令現場越黎幫少人<br />\n出唔到去應該尊重同支持<br />\n諗下點support<br />\n咩都做唔到都唔好令佢地打生打死完終於上到網發現啲兄弟屌佢衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地點忍心咁對佢地？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nAnyway 相信在場人士決定<br />\n但你地一定要小心同冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb343cfe10d0d0aad9258bbc5dae8444a5fa7f2","tid":1259483,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"自己推一下唔推了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2052476d68e069fc8eb441610312b628edeb53e9","tid":1259483,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzkqsX3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzkqsX3.png&h=494712d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家可以不同意<span style=\"color: teal;\">，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">但記得不譴責！</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"416a9b251fc6132a024dc1ab34a21930d99bced3","tid":1259483,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fb343cfe10d0d0aad9258bbc5dae8444a5fa7f2","tid":1259483,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":